title: Philippines GDP From Mining
description: GDP from Mining in Philippines decreased to 29331 PHP Million in the third quarter of 2022 from 43337 PHP Million in the second quarter of 2022. GDP from Mining in Philippines averaged 30452.34 PHP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 56863.46 PHP Million in the second quarter of 2019 and a record low of 12780.11 PHP Million in the second quarter of 2000. This page provides the latest reported value for - Philippines Gdp From Mining - plus previous releases, historical high and low, short-term forecast and long-term prediction, economic calendar, survey consensus and news.
author: Philippine Statistics Authority
